long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Extension to remove specific websites from the history. Just add domain name e.g. google, youtube, phub etc. No need for www, .com , .net and so on. It will run on the background periodically, set up interval that suits you more in settings. The default interval is 15 seconds.  

 Keeps the records of all visited websites separately. Also keep track of all the instances the chrome was opened.
